Nimbix,is,a,cloud,based,supercomputing,platform,It,is,aimed,at,meeting,big,data,processing,needs,for,diverse,industries,such,as,bioinformatics,finance,weather,and,climate,physics,and,more,Institutions,and,researchers,can,upload,all,of,their,information,or,feed,it,directly,to,NImbix,Then,with,instructions,from,the,user,Nimbix,will,process,all,of,the,data,behind,the,scenes,Nimbix,s,API,exposes,their,cloud,infrastructure,for,integrating,data,feeds